										<li id="comment-123586" class="commentbody"><div class="commenthead"><img alt='Stanislav Datskovskiy`s avatar' src='http://www.loper-os.org/avatar.png' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />								<div class="commentcount">14</div>
